{
  "stem": "26699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an intermediate school for another three years, which I spent to a proper government school called [non-English speech].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I was very proud about this because it was one of the leading schools of Bucharest, and it was named after one of the kings of Romania 500 years ago, 400 years ago, the great and the brave Michael.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lyonell, what was the political situation in Romania at the time?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, between the end of the war and 1948, it was a turmoil.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The country was occupied by the Russian troops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The communist party became very active and was supported by the Russian troops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other parties-- some of them were considered collaborators to the Nazis, and the democratic parties, the liberal and the peasant party, were very weak.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had also a king there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The king was very brave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Actually, I think that the Jews owe their salvation during the war through the balanced policy that the king conducted in Romania.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in this respect, I must be grateful for the King.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the king survived for a while all the pressures against him, and he managed to oppose a role switchover imposed by the Russian Army, which occupied the country-- not only liberated the country from the Germans, but occupied the country for their own sake.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 1948, the king abdicated-- was forced to abdicate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't want to abdicate, was forced to advocate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was expelled from Romania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Actually, he was lucky that wasn't executed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he went into exile to Switzerland, where he lives until now, and wasn't allowed until a couple of years ago-- he went to visit Romania.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
